OL,7,FWelby announced he was resigning on
OL,8,FNovember 12, after the Makin Review
OL,9,Fconcluded he failed to formally report
OL,10,Fabuse committed by John Smyth, who
OL,11,Fdied in 2018.
OL,13,FIn his final speech in the Lords,
OL,14,FJustin Welby said peers should feel
OL,15,Fsorry for his secretary following news
OL,16,Fhe would step down.
OL,18,F"If you pity anyone, pity my poor
OL,19,Fdiary secretary who has seen weeks and
OL,20,Fmonths of work disappear in a puff of
OL,21,Fa resignation announcement," he said.
