OL,7,F"I understand that my words - the
OL,8,Fthings that I said, and those I
OL,9,Fomitted to say - have caused further
OL,10,Fdistress for those who were
OL,11,Ftraumatised, and continue to be
OL,12,Fharmed, by John Smyth's heinous abuse,
OL,13,Fand by the far-reaching effects of
OL,14,Fother perpetrators of abuse.
OL,16,F"It did not intend to overlook the
OL,17,Fexperience of survivors or to make
OL,18,Flight of the situation ` and I am very
OL,19,Fsorry for having done so.
